data: {"jsonrpc":"2.0","id":2,"result":{"content":[{"type":"text","text":"## challenge://google-cloud/deploy\n\n| Astar Island | HTTPS endpoint (`/solve`) | Yes |\n| NorgesGruppen Data | Code upload (`.zip`) | No |\n\n\n========\n\n## challenge://norgesgruppen-data/examples\n\n# NorgesGruppen Data: Examples & Tips\n\n## Random Baseline\n\n========\n\n## challenge://norgesgruppen-data/overview\n\n# NorgesGruppen Data: Object Detection\n\nDetect grocery products on store shelves. Upload your model code as a `.zip` file — it runs in a sandboxed Docker container on our servers.\n\n========\n\n## challenge://norgesgruppen-data/scoring\n\n# NorgesGruppen Data: Scoring\n\n## Hybrid Scoring\n\n========\n\n## challenge://norgesgruppen-data/submission\n\n# NorgesGruppen Data: Submission Format\n\n## Zip Structure"}],"structuredContent":{"result":"## challenge://google-cloud/deploy\n\n| Astar Island | HTTPS endpoint (`/solve`) | Yes |\n| NorgesGruppen Data | Code upload (`.zip`) | No |\n\n\n========\n\n## challenge://norgesgruppen-data/examples\n\n# NorgesGruppen Data: Examples & Tips\n\n## Random Baseline\n\n========\n\n## challenge://norgesgruppen-data/overview\n\n# NorgesGruppen Data: Object Detection\n\nDetect grocery products on store shelves. Upload your model code as a `.zip` file — it runs in a sandboxed Docker container on our servers.\n\n========\n\n## challenge://norgesgruppen-data/scoring\n\n# NorgesGruppen Data: Scoring\n\n## Hybrid Scoring\n\n========\n\n## challenge://norgesgruppen-data/submission\n\n# NorgesGruppen Data: Submission Format\n\n## Zip Structure"},"isError":false}}

